                send "&e%{모르가나캐릭터::*}%" to {퍼시벌캐릭터::*}
            else if {모르가나캐릭터::*} is not true:
            
            
            play sound "minecraft:block.stone_button.click_off" with pitch 2 to player

            wait 50 tick
            console command "effect clear @a darkness"

            wait 45 tick

            console command "effect clear @a"
            console command "item replace entity @a armor.chest with minecraft:light_gray_stained_glass_pane[minecraft:equippable={slot:'chest',camera_overlay:'misc/addil2'}]"
            console command "stopsound @a * minecraft:item.armor.equip_generic"
            play sound "minecraft:13" with volume 0.2 to all players
            wait 3 seconds
            console command "item replace entity @a armor.chest with minecraft:air"

            give 1 paper named "&f대표 선정" to all players
            set {대표Timer::%uuid of player%} to 180
            set {대표MaxTimer::%uuid of player%} to 180
            create bossbar titled "&f[&9투표까지 남은 시간: &b%{대표Timer::%uuid of player%}%&9초&f]" and id "대표타이머" for all players with progress 100 with colors blue with style segmented 10

command 역할확인:
    trigger:
        send "멀린 %{멀린캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "퍼시벌 %{퍼시벌캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "암살자 %{암살자캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "모드레드 %{모드레드캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "모르가나 %{모르가나캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "오베론 %{오베론캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "기사(선) %{역할없음선캐릭터::*}%" to player
        send "기사(악) %{역할없음악캐릭터::*}%" to player

every 10 tick:
    if {역할확인종이} is true:
        loop all players:
            set slot 8 of inventory of loop-player to paper named "&f역할 확인"

every 10 tick:
    if {역할타이틀로확인} is true:
        send actionbar "♢" to {멀린캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "⁜" to {퍼시벌캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "€" to {암살자캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "£" to {오베론캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "¥" to {모르가나캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "©" to {모드레드캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "•" to {역할없음악캐릭터::*}
        send actionbar "®" to {역할없음선캐릭터::*}
    else:

every tick:
    loop all players:
        if {카드타이틀로확인::%loop-player%} is true:
            #send title "%{역할이름::%loop-player%}%" to loop-player
        else:

on inventory click:
    if name of event-item is "&f역할 확인":
        cancel event

on player's held item change:
    if {카드타이틀로확인::%player%} is true:
        delete {카드타이틀로확인::%player%}

on rightclick:
    if event-item is paper:
        if name of event-item contain "역할 확인":
            #send "%{카드타이틀로확인::%player%}%" to player
            if {카드타이틀로확인::%player%} is not true:
                set {카드타이틀로확인::%player%} to true
            else if {카드타이틀로확인::%player%} is true:
                delete {카드타이틀로확인::%player%}

every tick:
    loop all players:
        if {카드타이틀로확인::%loop-player%} is true:
            #send "1" to loop-player
            if {멀린캐릭터::*} contain loop-player:
                console command "item replace entity %loop-player% armor.feet with minecraft:light_gray_stained_glass_pane[minecraft:equippable={slot:'feet',camera_overlay:'misc/cardil1'}]"
            if {퍼시벌캐릭터::*} contain loop-player:
                console command "item replace entity %loop-player% armor.feet with minecraft:light_gray_stained_glass_pane[minecraft:equippable={slot:'feet',camera_overlay:'misc/cardil2'}]"
            if {암살자캐릭터::*} contain loop-player:
                console command "item replace entity %loop-player% armor.feet with minecraft:light_gray_stained_glass_pane[minecraft:equippable={slot:'feet',camera_overlay:'misc/cardil3'}]"
