                        send "{@시스템}%{접속카운트10}%님이 원정대에서 제거되었습니다" to {대표}
                        play sound "minecraft:block.stone_button.click_off" with pitch 2 to player
        
            else if event-item is paper:
                if size of {원정대구성원::*} is {원정대최대인원}:
                    close {대표}'s inventory
                    delete {투표수2}
                    console command "clear %{대표}% paper"
                    console command "item replace entity @a armor.chest with minecraft:light_gray_stained_glass_pane[minecraft:equippable={slot:'chest',camera_overlay:'misc/addil5'}]"
                    console command "stopsound @a * minecraft:item.armor.equip_generic"
                    play sound "minecraft:12" with volume 0.2 to all players
                    send "{@시스템}&e원정대 구성원 : %{원정대구성원::*}%" to all players
                    delete {원정대찬성투표}
                    delete {원정대반대투표}
                    wait 60 tick
                    console command "item replace entity @a armor.chest with air"
                    send "{@시스템}&e3초후 원정대 출발 찬반투표를 시작합니다" to all players
                    play sound "minecraft:block.stone_button.click_off" with pitch 2 to player
                    wait 1 second
                    send "{@시스템}&e2초후 원정대 출발 찬반투표를 시작합니다" to all players
                    play sound "minecraft:block.stone_button.click_off" with pitch 2 to player
                    wait 1 second
                    send "{@시스템}&e1초후 원정대 출발 찬반투표를 시작합니다" to all players
                    play sound "minecraft:block.stone_button.click_off" with pitch 2 to player
                    wait 1 second
                    
                    give 1 paper named "&f원정대 찬반투표" to all players
                    set {찬반Timer::%uuid of player%} to 300
                    set {찬반MaxTimer::%uuid of player%} to 300
                    create bossbar titled "&f[&9투표까지 남은 시간: &b%{찬반Timer::%uuid of player%}%&9초&f]" and id "찬반타이머" for all players with progress 100 with colors blue with style segmented 10

    if inventory name is "&c멀린을 지목하세요.":
