                    create bossbar titled "&f[&9투표까지 남은 시간: &b%{대표Timer::%uuid of player%}%&9초&f]" and id "대표타이머" for all players with progress 100 with colors blue with style segmented 10

command z찬반투표다음:
    trigger:
        if player is op:
            console command "clear @a paper"
            add 0 to {원정대찬성투표}
